{"tid":1702952,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"譚耀宗應該要死","createTime":"2019-11-10T04:30:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T08:02:40.000Z","uid":74778,"like":65,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"7cc8c889ab54ed7041c75e456effb498acae0939","tid":1702952,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T04:30:30.000Z","msg":"因為年紀大了，沒有理由不去死。<br />\n<br />\n<em><a href=\"https://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsID=20191110094551\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsID%3D20191110094551&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpkkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=bb0e90a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsID=20191110094551</a></em><br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委譚耀宗表示, 基本法清楚訂明, 特區要為23條立法, <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港已經回歸22年, 沒有理由不做,</span></strong> 但在近期的社會環境下, 要為基本法23條立法, 比之前更困難, 要留待中央和特區政府處理.<br />\n        譚耀宗出席電台節目時指, 他個人認為, 支持港獨的市場有限, 但近年有人不斷挑戰底線, 包括成立組織或政綱口號朝向自決, 隱含逐步搞港獨, 中央會認為, 如果一直沒有法律制止, 有人可能會有恃無恐.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ysDNMq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ysDNMq.gif&h=cdc59d1a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b532bd31dc710d0d82e5d5ce3a1189240273e90b","tid":1702952,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T04:41:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9b100b7df7906a16a7bd3d1ba6535ee29b9bf21","tid":1702952,"uid":82068,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T04:43:10.000Z","msg":"建制班友一路冇人搞<br />\n毛都冇少過仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7742a2d72a19ebb710554fabeb40a836a54e41","tid":1702952,"uid":4174,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T04:44:11.000Z","msg":"基本法都列明咗有普選 22 年了 